column6: Born in Tucson, Arizona, Raymond Pettibon came to prominence for his work in the punk rock scene in the 1980s. He is most well known for his creation of the Black Flag logo. His drawings are often comic-like in nature, but feature harsh and ironic text alongside the stark black and white images. It's not unusual for Pettibon to depict violent acts or include anti-authoritarian imagery in his art. In this deck, titled "Bang", he depicts a man holding a gun just after shooting a bird. An important figure in both the art and punk-rock scene, you'll definitely want to add this Supreme deck to your collection.

column6: Born in Tucson, Arizona, Raymond Pettibon came to prominence for his work in the punk rock scene in the 1980s. He is most well known for his creation of the Black Flag logo. His drawings are often comic-like in nature, but feature harsh and ironic text alongside the stark black and white images. It's not unusual for Pettibon to depict violent acts or include anti-authoritarian imagery in his art. In this deck, titled "Blood & Sperm", he depicts a police officer vomiting at a crime scene. An important figure in both the art and punk-rock scene, you'll definitely want to add this Supreme deck to your collection.

So if you are a fan of both luxury and art, StockX has got you covered!

column6: Go ahead, swoon. Virgil Abloh can do no wrong in our book. From his debut as the men’s art director for Louis Vuitton Spring Summer 2019, Abloh’s masterpiece of a trunk mini bag is already a cult favorite. Seen on celebrities and influencers worldwide, the design features the classic LV monogram print on a brown coated canvas. Black hardware cover the double zip closure system as well as the corner metal pieces. Bright orange and black matted chains latched on to the exterior zipper and on the sides to create a chain-link handle for a street-meets-luxury vibe.
